    "kit": {
      "info": {
        "contact": {
          "url": "https://imgflip.com/api"
        },
        "description": "RESTful JSON API for making memes with Imgflip's meme generator. Supports getting popular meme templates, captioning images and GIFs, searching memes, and AI-powered meme generation.",
        "servers": [
          {
            "description": "Imgflip API Server",
            "url": "https://api.imgflip.com"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Imgflip API",
        "version": "1.0.0",
        "tagline": "Generate memes programmatically: browse templates, caption images and GIFs, search, or create memes with AI",
        "homepage": "https://imgflip.com",
        "docs_url": "https://imgflip.com/api",
        "license_short": "Proprietary API operated by Imgflip LLC; free and Premium tiers, account credentials required for most endpoints",
        "license_md": "- Imgflip LLC operates the API; usage is subject to Imgflip's terms of service\n- Most endpoints require a valid Imgflip account (username + password) sent in the POST body\n- Free tier covers basic template listing and captioning (output is watermarked); Premium ($9.99/month) unlocks GIF captioning, search, AI meme generation, and watermark removal\n- Generated images are publicly accessible by URL and may be auto-deleted if unused; user-generated content is not curated",
        "about_md": "Imgflip API is the developer interface to [Imgflip](https://imgflip.com), the popular meme-generation site run by Imgflip LLC. It exposes a small, focused REST surface for building memes from templates, captioning still images and animated GIFs, searching a large template database, and synthesising new memes with AI.\n\nWhat you get from the API:\n\n- `GET /get_memes` — list of popular, captionable meme templates with their IDs, names, and dimensions\n- `POST /caption_image` — add text boxes to a template and receive the rendered meme URL\n- `POST /caption_gif` — caption animated GIF templates (Premium)\n- `POST /search_memes` — search across 1M+ templates by keyword (Premium)\n- `POST /get_meme` — fetch a specific meme template by ID (Premium)\n- `POST /automeme` and `POST /ai_meme` — auto-generate or AI-generate memes from text (Premium)\n\nAll requests are made over HTTPS to `https://api.imgflip.com`. Authentication uses an Imgflip account username and password posted in the request body (never in the URL). The free tier has no hard rate limit but may throttle abusive traffic; Premium plans include a monthly request allowance with small per-request overage fees. CORS is supported, so calls work directly from browser clients.",
        "entity_desc": {
          "free": "Endpoints available on the free tier, such as `GET /get_memes` for listing popular templates and `POST /caption_image` for rendering captioned memes (watermarked output).",
          "premium": "Endpoints that require a paid Imgflip Premium account, including `POST /caption_gif`, `POST /search_memes`, `POST /get_meme`, `POST /automeme`, and `POST /ai_meme`."
        },
        "auth": false
      },
